title: International Factball: Cameroon vs Chile
content: The QI Elves in association with www.visitengland.com bring you the seventh episode of this No Such Thing As A Fish Factball special - the only football podcast that has absolutely nothing to do with football. Today Dan Schreiber (@schreiberland), James Harkin (@jamesharkin), Jack Burke (@jacksburke) and Anna Ptaszynski (@nosuchthing) pit Cameroon against Chile to find out which is the most Quite Interesting country.
